data.description: This move-in-ready home might be what you've been looking for! Located in the beautiful Lake Nona area! You will find this gem inside the Randal Walk community.  It is a gated community  that features a private community pool and outdoor kitchen. This property features 3 specious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. walk-in closet and oversized closets, tray ceiling in master bedroom, Major appliances are included. This home is close to shopping and dining options, Medical City, VA Hospital, Nemours Hospital, UCF Medical Center, Adventhealth, Orlando MCO Airport, and major highways. Schedule your showing now!
